ries)|MacGyver]] (born in [[Ferndale, Michigan|Ferndale]]) * [[Patricia Ellis]], film actress of 1930s. ''[[The Case of the Lucky Legs]]'', ''[[Elmer, the Great]]'' (born in [[Birmingham, Michigan|Birmingham]]) * [[Eminem]] (Marshall Mathers III), rapper and actor, star of ''[[8 Mile (film)|8 Mile]]'' (born in [[Saint Joseph, Missouri]], raised in [[Warren, Michigan|Warren]]) * [[Jean Engstrom]], actress (born in Detroit, raised in [[Augusta, Michigan|Augusta]] and [[Battle Creek, Michigan|Battle Creek]]) * [[Venida Evans]], actress (born in [[Ypsilanti, Michigan|Ypsilanti]]; raised in Detroit) * [[Chad Everett]], actor, star of TV series ''[[Medical Center (TV series)|Medical Center]]'' and films such as ''[[The Singing Nun (film)|The Singing Nun]]'', ''[[Airplane II: The Sequel]]'' and ''[[Psycho (1998 film)|Psycho]]'' (born in [[South Bend, Indiana]], raised in [[Dearborn, Michigan|Dearborn]]) {{colend}}
